Class BasicList<T>

java.lang.Object
  cs.cscollections.lists.BasicList<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:

Direct Known Subclasses:
OrderedList, UnorderedList
public abstract class BasicList<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements ListADT<T>

The BasicList class provides a set of basic list operations that are used by all implementations list. There is no method to add elements to the class provided. The class is provided solely as an foundation for implementing list classes with a defined insertion scheme. Usable versions of the class include: - OrderedLinkedList - UnorderedLinkedList Note: The type corresponding to T must implement the comparable interface.
